00:40:13,652 --> 00:40:18,152
That's right, it is finally time to start Day 2!

54
00:40:18,652 --> 00:40:20,652
Is everyone hyped!?

55
00:40:22,652 --> 00:40:25,652
All right, before we kick things off, of course,

56
00:40:25,652 --> 00:40:29,152
we have some important safety rules and house guidelines to go over.

57
00:40:29,652 --> 00:40:32,952
First, photography and the use of recording equipment

58
00:40:32,952 --> 00:40:36,152
are strictly prohibited during the performance.

59
00:40:36,352 --> 00:40:39,652
However, if you are watching from home, screenshots are allowed.

60
00:40:39,652 --> 00:40:42,152
Please take lots of screenshots!

61
00:40:42,352 --> 00:40:45,152
Yeah, スクショはOKですよ！
Yeah, screenshots are okay!

62
00:40:45,652 --> 00:40:49,652
Also, the venue is smoke-free, so please refrain from smoking inside.

63
00:40:50,152 --> 00:40:53,152
Unless you're smoking hot like me!

64
00:40:53,352 --> 00:40:55,652
Mm, where have I heard that one before? / Someone said that yesterday!

65
00:40:57,152 --> 00:41:01,652
If you start unfeeling- feeling unwell at any point,

66
00:41:01,652 --> 00:41:03,652
please don't push yourself.

67
00:41:03,852 --> 00:41:08,152
Just reach out to the nearest staff member for help.

68
00:41:08,152 --> 00:41:10,652
And drink water!

69
00:41:11,152 --> 00:41:15,652
For everyone's safety, please avoid any dangerous or disruptive behavior.

70
00:41:15,852 --> 00:41:20,152
This, once again, no matter how hyped it is,

71
00:41:20,152 --> 00:41:23,952
includes moshing, diving, sitting on shoulders,

72
00:41:23,952 --> 00:41:29,152
jumping excessively, or throwing objects toward the stage.

73
00:41:30,152 --> 00:41:33,152
Climbing onto the stage, intentionally blocking the aisles,

74
00:41:33,152 --> 00:41:36,152
or rushing toward the front is also not allowed.

75
00:41:36,652 --> 00:41:40,152
Please refrain from disruptive shouting,

76
00:41:40,152 --> 00:41:43,152
erratic lightstick movements, or any extreme motions

77
00:41:43,152 --> 00:41:46,152
that might interfere with the experience of those around you.

78
00:41:46,652 --> 00:41:47,652
Be considerate.

79
00:41:48,152 --> 00:41:52,652
If you don't follow the instructions of our staff or the venue staff,

80
00:41:52,652 --> 00:41:55,152
you may be asked to leave the venue.

81
00:41:55,352 --> 00:41:59,152
Yeah, please keep in mind that the venue, organizers,

82
00:41:59,152 --> 00:42:03,652
performers, and staff cannot be held responsible for any accident,

83
00:42:03,652 --> 00:42:07,152
equipment damage, or trouble caused by failing to follow instructions.

84
00:42:07,352 --> 00:42:10,152
I- you stumbled over the same words!

85
00:42:10,352 --> 00:42:15,152
It's hard, okay? I'm trying my best here. I can't read!

86
00:42:15,652 --> 00:42:19,652
Additionally, any cost for damage resulting from ignoring these rules

87
00:42:19,652 --> 00:42:22,652
will be the responsibility of the person involved.

88
00:42:23,152 --> 00:42:27,152
There are cameras in the venue for filming and photography today,

89
00:42:27,152 --> 00:42:30,652
and you might appear in the footage or photos.

90
00:42:31,152 --> 00:42:36,652
These may be used for promotional purposes later on, so please keep that in mind.

91
00:42:37,152 --> 00:42:41,652
And finally, just like yesterday, the concert will be in two parts.

92
00:42:42,152 --> 00:42:46,652
There's a part for Wawa and there's a part for me, so please look forward to both of them!

93
00:42:51,652 --> 00:42:53,652
And yeah, that is it for the rules! Woohoo!

94
00:42:54,152 --> 00:42:58,652
The show is about to begin, so get ready!

95
00:42:59,152 --> 00:43:03,652
Have fun! Have fun! See you soon! Bye bye!

