272
00:59:43,873 --> 00:59:48,573
Woo! Hello everyone!

273
00:59:48,573 --> 00:59:54,373
It is Day 2 of "Drawn to Dawn"!

274
00:59:57,873 --> 01:00:05,373
Yes, yes, welcome to Day 2 of Takanashi Kiara and Ninomae Ina'nis's first concert, "Drawn to Dawn"!

275
01:00:05,896 --> 01:00:07,396
Are you guys enjoying the show so far?

276
01:00:12,396 --> 01:00:14,896
Ah, you know, um, I was really...

277
01:00:14,896 --> 01:00:18,396
