282
01:00:35,396 --> 01:00:39,396
So I hope you guys had fun singing it! Thank you again!

283
01:00:43,396 --> 01:00:46,396
And of course, I sang two of my Senpai's songs...

284
01:00:46,396 --> 01:00:50,896
um, Sencho's Dead Man's Chest and Hoshimachi's Palette.

285
01:00:54,396 --> 01:00:58,896
I specifically... (stammers) I specifically wanted to choose their songs because...

286
01:00:59,396 --> 01:01:06,896
um, they're, you know, Senpais that I really look up to and...

287
01:01:07,896 --> 01:01:11,896
I always feel like my journey here wouldn't have

288
01:01:11,896 --> 01:01:16,396
been possible if I didn't discover my Senpais many, many years ago.

289
01:01:18,896 --> 01:01:22,896
And I always, you know, wanted to pay respect

290
01:01:22,896 --> 01:01:25,896
